Structure:

index.php - login/register page

mundial.php - main page handles login, shows current games with live score and updates database when they finish

apostas.php - page that shows the list of bets made by user

campeao.php - special page for the bets on the world champion

config.php - includes database info

grupos.php - page that shows the classification in the 8 world cup groups

insere_jogo.html/php - insert games into the database

jogo.php - allow betting / show livescore for a specific game

logout.php - self explanatory

registar.php - registration script

regulamento.html - regulations for participation

sorttable.js - javascript that allows sorting html tables by column

table.php - shows table with statistics about users

update.php / updatetable.php - update user scores and bet number when something goes wrong
